gfxeditor.shapes

Class Rectangle

  • java.lang.Object
    • gfxeditor.Shape
      • gfxeditor.shapes.Rectangle
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable

    public class Rectangle
extends Shape
    This shape represents a rectangle. It internally uses a java.awt.geom.Rectangle2D object and is automatically enumerated, starting at 1.
